OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showers
OL,6,Fmay linger into the evening across
OL,7,Fnorthern and western parts, before
OL,8,Fslowly fading. Otherwise most other
OL,9,Fareas dry with clear spells and light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,13,Fincreasingly bright, with sunny spells
OL,14,Flikely across the region. Winds mostly
OL,15,Flight but breezy at times towards the
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
