OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand showery rain during Thursday
OL,7,Fclearing by early afternoon, then
OL,8,Fbright, Friday and Saturday probably
OL,9,Fmostly dry and breezy, with clear or
OL,10,Fsunny spells. Temperatures mostly
OL,11,Fabove average throughout.
